  [2]: http://www.genome.jp/kegg/soap/
  [3]: http://www.brenda-enzymes.org/soap/
  [4]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_Services_Description_Language
  [5]: http://ws.apache.org/axis2/
  [6]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SOAP
